<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Work-Zone</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .navbar .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        .navbar .logo span {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .navbar .menu {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .navbar .menu a {
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .navbar .menu a:hover {
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        .navbar .menu .profile-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        .hero {
            background-color: #444;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .collaboration-area {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .collaboration-area {
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .chat-box {
            height: 400px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .chat-box .messages {
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .chat-box .messages p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .chat-box .chat-input {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .chat-box .chat-input input {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .chat-box .chat-input button {
            background-color: #ff6600;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .chat-box .chat-input button:hover {
            background-color: #e65c00;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .footer .footer-content {
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        .footer .footer-content h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff6600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer .footer-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer .footer-content .social-icons {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer .footer-content .social-icons a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .footer .footer-content .social-icons a:hover {
            color: #ff6600; 
        }
        .footer .footer-bottom {
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .project-section {
            background-color: #444; 
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 100%; 
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center;
        }
        .project-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: #333; 
            color: #f5f5f5; 
            width: 100%; 
        }
        .project-box h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
        }
        .project-grid {
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); 
            gap: 20px; 
            width: 100%; 
        }
        .project-item {
            height: 100px; 
            background-color: #444; 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none; 
            color: inherit;
        }
        .project-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05); 
        }
        .project-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ff6600; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">
            Work-Zone
        </div>
        <div class="menu">
            <a href="/products">Project Ideas</a>
            <a href="/collab">Collaboration</a>
            <a href="/about">Service</a>
            <a href="/user">User</a>
            <i class="fas fa-user-circle profile-icon"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Work-Zone</h1>
        <p>Collaborate with others and engage in real-time discussions. Start a project or join an existing one. Connect with your peers and make the most of our platform.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="project-section">
        <div class="project-box">
            <h2>Projects</h2>
            <div class="project-grid">
                <a href="/products1" class="project-item">
                    <h3>Frontend Project</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="/products2" class="project-item">
                    <h3>Backend Project</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="/products3" class="project-item">
                    <h3>C++ Project</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="/products4" class="project-item">
                    <h3>Python Project</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="/products5" class="project-item">
                    <h3>Java Project</h3>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <footer>
            <div class="footer-content">
                <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
                <p>Subscribe to our newsletter and follow us on social media to stay updated with the latest news and updates.</p>
                <div class="social-icons">
                    <a href="#" class="fab fa-facebook-f" title="Facebook"></a>
                    <a href="#" class="fab fa-twitter" title="Twitter"></a>
                    <a href="#" class="fab fa-linkedin-in" title="LinkedIn"></a>
                    <a href="#" class="fab fa-instagram" title="Instagram"></a>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-bottom">
                    &copy; 2024 Work-Zone. All rights reserved.
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
